<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Action Expired - MC Quote</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #f5f5f5;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #333;
    }
    .box {
      background: #fff;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 80px auto;
      box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 24px;
      color: #c00;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    a {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 10px 18px;
      background: #007bff;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .box { padding: 20px; }
      h1 { font-size: 20px; }
      p, a { font-size: 14px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="box">
    <h1>Action Expired</h1>
    <p>This link is no longer active. It may have already been used or the job has been removed.</p>
    <p>If you still need assistance, feel free to submit a new job request.</p>
    <a href="/">Return to Homepage</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
